close_reason: "Completed: pm-changelog 2026.5.24-12 adds package-owned --all-release-tags full historical changelog generation from git release tag windows, exposes it through CLI and pm extension contracts, documents it, passes release:check and linked pm evidence, and is published to npm/GitHub release."
